name: kathy crub
text: The only way i would come to this place is for food that tastes like its 4 days old the crust even shows with how light,doughy and thin it is. It doesn't look like any other pizza i got from other locations. I would strongly advise to go anywhere else, this place is not worth it.

name: Darren Murphy
text: Terrible quality food compared to other locations.

text: We have tried this place MULTIPLE times, even though half the time pizza is burnt and the price you get online when placing the order is always a few cents off from the total they say at the door, which I can never understand why. Anyways …More

name: Leandra DeLeon
text: Pizza always comes out great, however sometimes the employees are so rude they don't even greet you or say have a good day when you leave. One time I got points for a free medium pizza and one of the workers gave me attitude because I …More

name: Cameron Schultze
text: Pretty good chicken and pizza hut always has that good sauce for dipping your bread sticks.

name: Terry Hubbard
text: Started going here because dominos went down hill now this place is bad. Last few times my order was messed up they threw topping on after it came out of oven and in will never be going back. I contacted them and the manager never called very disappointing.

name: Brooke Kelly
text: Waited 2 hours for our order and when we finally got it it was missing the wings in the big box and the pizza was cold. The driver was bawling and complaining about a bad experience at the first place she delivered. It was fine we just …More

name: Chris Coen
text: Fast friendly,  a little on the rough side at 745 on a Sunday night...

name: Matt Schmidt
text: Absolutely abysmal. Steer clear. My order was 2 pizzas and two types of boneless wings and fries. Some how they managed to make all of them gross. The pizzas we received were dried out, like they had sat there for ages, because between the …More

name: D Christine
text: Pizza was very burnt.. luckily I like things crispy.. my family.. not so much lol

name: KPM Lakewood
text: Mark Vigil is always awesome to me and my family. He is always courteous, kind and pleasant to speak with.  The food is always hot and fresh, and ALWAYS right, every time! Good job Mark and crew!!

name: Lance Cochran
text: We had the best pizza we've had in a long time from this location.  The service for our carry out order was great. Ordering online was very convenient.

name: n despain
text: Way understaffed. Service was slow, food came with more sauce and no cheese. When I asked for cheese...said they would remake it ..  then it took over an hour with others waiting the same length of time.

name: Joseph Vespoli
text: Good pizza

name: Elizabeth Garcia
text: Would give them a 4 if their food came out a bit better. Other then that everything else is ok. Just ok. Only pizza place I'll order from in the area sadly and it's average at the least.

name: Evan Lemke
text: I live in Leyden Rock less than a mile away, but the website says there are no delivery options available.  You can call over the phone and they have no problem delivering, but wont honor any of the online coupons.  Im going to leave this review here until they fix the website.
